message.content:
```bash
cat <<'EOF' > config/api-gateway.yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: api-gateway
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: api-gateway
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: api-gateway
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: gateway
        image: nginx:1.25
        ports:
        - containerPort: 80
        volumeMounts:
        - name: config-volume
          mountPath: /etc/nginx/conf.d
          readOnly: true
      volumes:
      - name: config-volume
        configMap:
          name: api-gateway-config
---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: api-gateway
spec:
  selector:
    app: api-gateway
  ports:
    - protocol: TCP
      port: 80
      targetPort: 80
  type: ClusterIP
EOF
```
